{"tid":1196354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"真係一日未燒到埋身 都冇人係會肯盡地一舖","createTime":"2019-06-09T19:04:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-09T19:22:44.000Z","uid":138728,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"53e0a847bfea203efc02dec5f34a048eb84d1dfb","tid":1196354,"uid":138728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T19:04:59.000Z","msg":"唔係想潑冷水<br />\n但係問心 當一個人擁有得愈多 風險就愈大愈多野輸<br />\n當我地未去到03經濟輸到仆街<br />\n05韓農飯都冇得開既地步<br />\n就想叫人一齊衝擊 佔領<br />\n再加上有曬前車之鑑<br />\n除左一眾義士之外根本冇足夠既人會支持<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以一齊罷工罷市啦屌你老母</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你地完全冇風險呀<br />\n可唔可以用一兩日人工去驗證下香港仲有冇得救呀<br />\n係咪要真係想等到燒到埋身<br />\n係咪真係想用鮮血抗爭呀<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">醒下啦 香港人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r81yTXw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr81yTXw.png&h=ab5bbea4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d4bbe84ff0790f43361562e1be72f91233978ad0","tid":1196354,"uid":138728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T19:09:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac81899575322f6a50d03a16cc5a834feb8542e7","tid":1196354,"uid":138728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T19:11:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f270e087acb95f21f960b6685ecc72b5fb11bc01","tid":1196354,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T19:12:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a4052036696becf8cb9a9e580859853ca791146","tid":1196354,"uid":